did.unittitle: Rockefeller University records, Dissertations of Students

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Records more than 25 years old are open for research. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of RAC.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Information regarding the Rockefeller Archive Center's preferred elements and forms of citation can be found at http://www.rockarch.org/research/citations.php

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Minimal processing. Some material remains in original housing.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Consists of doctoral dissertations of students who attended the Rockefeller Institute/Rockefeller University.
